snippet.title: Amber Heard Trolls Australian Deputy PM Barnaby Joyce
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is getting the last laugh at Australian politician Barnaby Joyce who coerced Heard and then-husband Johnny Depp into filming a video apology for illegally smuggling her dogs into the country. Now, Joyce is facing his own legal scandal and Heard can’t help but troll Australia’s Deputy Prime Minister.
